OL,3,CCharity say goalie should have been
OL,4,Csubstituted straight after collision
OL,6,FHowever, Ederson did not immediately
OL,7,Fleave the field and played on for
OL,8,Fseveral minutes before being replaced
OL,9,Fby seconf-choice 'keeper Stefan Ortega.
OL,11,FLuke Griggs, the chief executive of
OL,12,Fthe brain injury charity Headway,
OL,13,Fsaid: "The fundamental principle of
OL,14,Fany concussion protocol is 'if in
OL,15,Fdoubt, sit it out.'
