OL,3,CCharity say goalie should have been
OL,4,Csubstituted straight after collision
OL,6,F"The concern from players of both
OL,7,Fteams in the immediate aftermath of
OL,8,Fthe injury, as well as from the
OL,9,Fmedical team and the fact a stretcher
OL,10,Fwas brought on to the pitch, would
OL,11,Fsuggest a clear concern for Ederson's
OL,12,Fwell-being.
OL,14,F"The fact that he was not immediately
OL,15,Fremoved would suggest a concussion was
OL,16,Fnot suspected. This is hard to
OL,17,Funderstand, especially as symptoms can
OL,18,Fbe delayed in their presentation.
