OL,3,CCharity say goalie should have been
OL,4,Csubstituted straight after collision
OL,6,F"While we were relieved to see the
OL,7,Fplayer taken off a few minutes later,
OL,8,Fit is hard to fathom why this was not
OL,9,Fan immediate decision.
OL,11,F"It is yet another example of when a
OL,12,Ftemporary concussion substitute would
OL,13,Fhave been helpful."
