OL,6,FThe Premier League has sought to trial
OL,7,Ftemporary concussion substitutes, but
OL,8,Fthis has been repeatedly refused by
OL,9,Fthe game's lawmakers in favour of
OL,10,Ftrials of additional permanent
OL,11,Fconcussion subs, which will become a
OL,12,Fpermanent option for competitions to
OL,13,Fadopt from July 1.
OL,15,FEderson was visibly upset and angry
OL,16,Fafter being taken off in what was a
OL,17,Fcrucial game for his club, kicking out
OL,18,Fat some water bottles close to the
OL,19,FCity technical area.
