OL,3,CCharity say goalie should have been
OL,4,Csubstituted straight after collision
OL,6,F"Ederson's angry reaction is no
OL,7,Fsurprise given the competitive nature
OL,8,Fof players who want to take part in
OL,9,Fmassive games like this one, though
OL,10,Fhis reaction underscores the need to
OL,11,Ftake such decisions out of the
OL,12,Fplayers' hands," Griggs added.
OL,14,FGuardiola said after the match:
OL,15,F"Ederson has a kick in the eye and it
OL,16,Fis swollen. He could not see properly.
OL,17,FThe doctor came to me and said, 'Pep,
OL,18,Fhe cannot see properly and he has to
OL,19,Fbe replaced'.
