OL,6,F"When the doctor says that, I don't
OL,7,Fhave an alternative."
OL,9,FCity and the Premier League have been
OL,10,Fcontacted for comment. Ederson's
OL,11,Freplacement Ortega went on to make
OL,12,Fseveral key saves as City won 2-0 in
OL,13,FLondon to put them in pole position to
OL,14,Fsecure the title on Sunday 19 May.
